Class JAXRPCClassFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.xml.rpc.util.JAXRPCClassFactory
  • public class JAXRPCClassFactory
extends Object
    Singleton factory class to instantiate concrete classes based on the jaxrpc version to be used to generate the code.
    Author:
    JAX-RPC Development Team
